{"tid":1717913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家緊記抗爭嘅目標，對準目標","createTime":"2019-11-13T17:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T17:12:23.000Z","uid":289493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ad22ff08f4f1f53e6e0544036d295ea708b5be","tid":1717913,"uid":289493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:12:23.000Z","msg":"請大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>顧及無辜</strong></span></span>：唔好玩火魔，唔好高空擲物，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>以免傷及無辜、甚至接放學嘅家長</strong></span></span>；<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>保持清醒、冷靜</strong></span></span>：分清邊啲做得，邊啲唔做得，都<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好俾位狗入</strong></span></span>，俾佢哋做衰嘢嫁禍大家；<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>保護自己安全</strong></span></span>：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好玩軍營</strong></span></span>，好易死人；<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>保持運動嘅認受性</strong></span></span>：<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>民意、輿論</strong></span></span>都已好明顯喺我哋呢邊，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔好俾佢逆轉</strong></span></span>。"}]}